│ causing an assertion in `ScalarEvolution`.                                                 │
│                                                                                            │
│ My previous attempts to fix this by adding checks in `LoopPredication` were correct in     │
│ principle but failed because the associated test case, `pr117537.ll`, has a `FileCheck`    │
